## Constraints
*   Requires store selection before toggle can be enabled.
*   Manual input only possible if toggle is OFF.
*   Sync dependent on store address data integrity.
## Assumptions
*   Merchants will have at least one store created in most cases.
*   Merchants want flexibility between auto and manual setup.
*   Store location is always a valid and complete address.
## Acceptance Criteria

| **AC ID** | **Scenario** | **Condition** | **Expected Result** |
| ---| ---| ---| --- |
| AC-PU01 | Auto-populate ON | Store selected, toggle ON | Pickup address auto-filled from store, shown as read-only, success toast on Save |
| AC-PU02 | Store update sync | Store address updated, toggle ON | Pickup address updates automatically |
| AC-PU03 | Toggle ON w/o store | Store not selected, toggle ON | Error toast: “Please select a store.” Toggle stays OFF |
| AC-PU04 | Multiple stores | Store switched (toggle ON) | Pickup address updates to new store, confirm update |
| AC-PU05 | Store deleted | Linked store removed (toggle ON) | Pickup address invalid, error in shipping settings: “Please select store.” |
| AC-PU06 | Disable toggle | Toggle ON → OFF | Auto-filled values cleared, manual fields enabled |
| AC-PU07 | Re-enable toggle | Toggle OFF → ON after manual entry | Manual address discarded, confirm overwrite before applying store address |
| AC-PU08 | No store exists | Merchant has no store | Toggle disabled, tooltip: “Please add a store to enable auto-populate.” |

